In this lesson,

137
00:11:27,652 --> 00:11:32,030
we discuss the basic security
concepts in cyber-physical systems.

138
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:37,890
Namely, confidentiality,
integrity and availability.

139
00:11:37,890 --> 00:11:41,744
We also learn about potential
attacks against them.

140
